    <item>
      <title>美国大使称美国及其盟友的贸易联盟使中国陷入孤立</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/us-and-allies-trade-coalition-isolates-china-ambassador-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻日本大使表示，美国与其盟友之间的贸易联盟正在帮助孤立中国。他补充说，无论谁赢得总统大选，华盛顿在印度洋-太平洋地区的多边主义方针都可能继续存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/us-and-allies-trade-coalition-isolates-china-ambassador-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 03:24:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言取消居住在海外的美国人的所得税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/trump-vows-to-eliminate-income-taxes-on-americans-living-abroad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将取消对居住在其他国家的美国人征收的美国所得税，这是 2024 年竞选最后阶段一系列税收提案中的最新提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/trump-vows-to-eliminate-income-taxes-on-americans-living-abroad</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 02:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰领导人与拜登讨论中东和北爱尔兰问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/irish-leader-biden-discuss-middle-east-northern-ireland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰总理西蒙·哈里斯在谈到周三与总统乔·拜登的通话时表示，白宫为庆祝美爱建交一百周年举行的会议讨论了对中东冲突的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/irish-leader-biden-discuss-middle-east-northern-ireland</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 00:20:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将公布工会和企业争论不休的工人权利法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/uk-to-publish-workers-rights-bill-fought-over-by-unions-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默领导的英国新政府周四公布了一系列新的工人权利措施，这是工党在选举获胜宣言中做出的关键承诺之一，旨在平衡工党过去四年来一直在争取的工会和商界领袖之间的相互竞争的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/uk-to-publish-workers-rights-bill-fought-over-by-unions-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>抵押贷款巨头呼吁资金来劝说英国老年人减少住房规模</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/mortgage-giant-calls-for-money-to-coax-older-britons-to-downsize</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最大的抵押贷款机构之一呼吁大臣们采取财政激励措施，说服老年人缩小住房规模，释放数百万套房产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/mortgage-giant-calls-for-money-to-coax-older-britons-to-downsize</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔诺沃亚在每日停电中任命新能源部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/ecuador-s-noboa-names-new-energy-minister-amid-daily-blackouts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔总统丹尼尔·诺沃亚在任职 10 个月内任命了第四位能源部长，因为政府在数周的严重停电之后仍不得不扩大每日停电范围。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/ecuador-s-noboa-names-new-energy-minister-amid-daily-blackouts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 21:39:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
